@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: Researcher Views All Research

actor Researcher
participant "Frontend/UI" as UI
participant "Backend/API" as API
participant "Auth Middleware (JWT)" as AUTH
database "Database (Neon)" as DB

== Load Researcher Homepage ==

Researcher -> UI: Navigate to 'Researcher Homepage'
UI -> API: GET /trl/case (JWT)
UI -> API: GET /trl/appointment (JWT)

API -> AUTH: Verify JWT & role=Researcher
AUTH --> API: Valid / Invalid

alt Invalid Token
    API --> UI: 401 Unauthorized
    UI --> Researcher: Redirect to Login
else Valid
    API -> DB: Fetch all research cases
    API -> DB: Fetch appointment summary
    API -> DB: Aggregate statistics
    DB --> API: Return aggregated data
    API --> UI: 200 OK (Dashboard Data)
end

UI --> Researcher: Display research list
UI --> Researcher: Display appointment stats
UI --> Researcher: Display summary cards

@enduml